comments: Dr. Rutti is an awesome professor. She takes a different route when it comes to lecturing and her teaching style. While it may seem that she is lazy and super laid back, I probably learned the most from her classes over many of my other professors. She is very into team projects during class time and keeps everyone involved.

Very easy A if you just read the book. Some might even get an A just by reading the chapter summaries. Not an exciting or highly information class/teacher.
